**Story**

Once upon a time in a forest,there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree, which was on a banks of river. 
In the same forest there lived a Crocodile and his wife. 
One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.The kind hearted monkey affered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them. As days passed by the crocodile and monkey became good friends....
